RT EseMonday.eth 🥑
Hi everyone 👋🏼
Are you tired of gas fees on Ethereum being pricey and unstable? 😔
@gashawkio has a solution that saves up to 95% on the transaction fees with it's easy-to-use platform
it's a non-custodial service that works on Ethereum, Optimism and the Base network with more chains coming soon.
I've put together a short tutorial show you how to get a started with @gashawkio 
Get started 👉🏼 :  https://www.gashawk.io/
Disclaimer: This video is in partnership with @Tunnl_io , the very first on-chain creator marketplace
Like , Comment , and Share!
